snippet.textDisplay:
I wanted to share why each of you are important to me and how each 1 of you helped me.

Eugene - you helped me come out to my family. You helped me be myself when I was afraid. You helped me love myself. Thank you for being one of the only out, Korean YouTubers. I love you and I aspire to be like you. I am also Korean 😊

Ned - you helped me own up to the fact that I'm a complete nerd. You helped me be comfortable with my level of knowledge on topics. Thank you. I love you.

Keith - you helped me love the fact that I like food. Your eat the menu series helps me know what food to eat in America, because I'm new to America. Thank you. I love you.

Zach - you helped me embrace my humor and my health issues. I am so thankful for that. I will love you forever and always.

Each try guys has helped a ton. And I will always be thankful. I love each and every one of you. You mean so much to me. I discovered your channel when I fell into a deep depression. You guys helped me see the light at the end of the tunnel. Thank you so much. I love you all.
